rComments: Felt like he was only teaching the first row of the class sometimes. I also dont really like his powerpoint slides His midterm was hard

Lectures were jam-packed with content and initially, I found it a bit intimidating. However, Ron has a great way of explaining things and does his best to explain topics in a simple manner. He goes over multiple practice problems every lecture which helps in understanding concepts. On the downside, assignments are due weekly and are very tricky.

teacherRatingTags: ['Lecture heavy', 'Get ready to read', 'Clear grading criteria']
